text: Pete Rodriguez may refer to: * Pete Rodriguez (American football) (1940–2014), American football coach * Pete "El Conde" Rodríguez (1932–2000), Puerto Rican salsa singer * Pete Rodriguez (boogaloo musician) (born 1932), leader and pianist of a Puerto Rican boogaloo band * Pete Rodriguez (jazz musician) (born 1969), jazz trumpeter and percussionist
title: Pete Rodriguez
